:: Grab that cozy love seat in the corner {"position":"800,200","size":"100,100"}
A plush, slightly faded along the edges, ruby velour fabric sinks gently as your fingertips brush against the arm rest. It's not only cozy, it gives you a great vantage point of the cafe at large. An extremely attractive, black apron clad human appears in your line of sight, hands you a menu and raises an eyebrow...

